title: Canberra weather in February 2026 | Canberra 14 day weather
text: The temperatures in Canberra in February are comfortable with low of 13°C and and high up to 26°C. You can expect about 3 to 8 days of rain in Canberra during the month of February. It’s a good idea to bring along your umbrella so that you don’t get caught in poor weather. Our weather forecast can give you a great sense of what weather to expect in Canberra in February 2026. If you’re planning to visit Canberra in the near future, we highly recommend that you review the 14 day weather forecast for Canberra before you arrive.
